definitions.definition: Used in the names of units of volume formed by multiplying a unit of length by itself twice.
Relating to polynomials of the form a x 3 + b x 2 + c x + d {\displaystyle ax^{3}+bx^{2}+cx+d} .
Having three equal axes and all angles 90°.
